{
  "stem": "8.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Upon our arrival, they either took away or killed all the young children, so that they made space for us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The place was much more homey than Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had barracks, and we had bunk beds where we slept.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But the work was unbearable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We had to hew stones out of mines.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We had to build roads.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We had to take apart a Jewish cemetery and use it to build the roads with it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we had to carry heavy loads of, of German uniforms over ravines over a plank, and we were told to run.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And if we couldn't hold our balance, we would fall, fall in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We were also suffering from malnutrition, and we had boils all over our bodies, and had bed bugs that would then sit on these boils.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And by this time, we lost so much weight that our, our cheeks were sunken in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And sometimes we had bed bugs making nests in our cheeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were here for about, about two months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And the Russian army was getting closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And there were cannons and shootings almost every night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And there were also [INAUDIBLE] often for the purpose of witnessing hangings of those that tried to get away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "There was one boy that I met one day when I was rummaging through the garbage and looking for a pot.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And that reminds me, it may have been a one of Schindler's pots.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he-- and because this was where Schindler's movie took place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I, I was whipped by an officer, a German officer, because I was talking to this young man.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I started to cry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he told me, don't you ever cry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Don't you ever show them that it hurts.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
